        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks FJP for his review which CD has received and read. There have been many reviews in England opposed to CD but FJP’s is "the single one which seems … <hi rend="italic">perfectly</hi> fair &amp; just &amp; candid". The only difference between them is that CD "attaches much more weight to the explanation of facts, &amp; somewhat less weight to the difficulties" than FJP. "I always jump at any theory which groups &amp; explains facts".</p>  
<p>Would be proud to send FJP a copy of his <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
